			<p class="text-center text-[0.8125rem] text-gray-400 font-light mt-8">
				Flat pricing. No per-package, per-SKU, or per-location fees.
			</p>
		</section>

		<!-- FAQ -->
		<section class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
			<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
				<div class="font-mono text-[0.7rem] text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 text-center">FAQ</div>
				<h2 class="text-[1.5rem] font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-10 text-center">Questions about pricing</h2>

				<div class="divide-y divide-gray-200">

					<details class="py-5 group">
						<summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none">
							<span class="text-[0.9375rem] font-medium text-gray-900">Do I need a credit card to start the trial?</span>
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
						</summary>
						<p class="mt-3 text-[0.875rem] text-gray-500 font-light leading-[1.75]">
							No. Your 14-day free trial starts the moment you create an account — no credit card, no commitment. If you decide to continue after the trial, you'll choose a billing plan at that point.
						</p>
					</details>

					<details class="py-5 group">
						<summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none">
							<span class="text-[0.9375rem] font-medium text-gray-900">What happens when the trial ends?</span>
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
						</summary>
						<p class="mt-3 text-[0.875rem] text-gray-500 font-light leading-[1.75]">
							At the end of your 14-day trial you'll be prompted to choose a plan to continue. Your data stays intact — nothing is deleted.
						</p>
					</details>

					<details class="py-5 group">
						<summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none">
							<span class="text-[0.9375rem] font-medium text-gray-900">Can I switch between monthly and annual billing?</span>
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400 shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
						</summary>
						<p class="mt-3 text-[0.875rem] text-gray-500 font-light leading-[1.75]">
							Yes. You can switch from monthly to annual billing at any time to lock in the lower rate. Switching from annual to monthly takes effect at the end of your current billing period.
						</p>
					</details>

					<details class="py-5 group">
